A transformer thief has met his ugly end after trying to steal from a transformer in Abuja. A Nigerian man has had his life cut short in a sad manner after he attempted to steal from a transformer in Abuja. It was gathered that the sad incident took place yesterday in Kuje area of the country’s capital while it was raining. The corpse of the thief was later removed with other equipment he had come with for the operation. Watch video below: Man electrocuted while trying to steal from a transformer during the rain, yesterday, in #Kuje, #Abuja A post shared by  Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) on Jul 29, 2019 at 11:20pm PDT Source